{"tid":872670,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦開機後上唔到網 應用程式開唔到","createTime":"2018-10-23T01:38:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T13:36:05.000Z","uid":86026,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0ee5da3eedb21ff052a4d08aba5ca7844d78b72f","tid":872670,"uid":86026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T01:38:20.000Z","msg":"電腦係window 7系統<br />\n本身部機得個過左期的nod32<br />\n幾個月前中左網上d廣告毒<br />\n無理過佢<br />\n呢幾日部腦laglag地<br />\n有時禁d apps 無反應<br />\n<br />\n就諗住del左舊nod32 <br />\n上網裝返個免費版掃下毒<br />\n之後掃左7個威脅<br />\n6個delete左<br />\n<br />\n之後部電腦就用唔到咁濟<br />\n入到桌面<br />\n上唔到網<br />\n禁d 應用程式野無反應（好似所有要系統管理員身份既apps都無反應）<br />\nCtrl alt delete 無反應<br />\n只係開到d files    我的電腦 控制台個d<br />\n但就算開到都會好lag...<br />\n<br />\n試過用系統還原 <br />\n但情況無變<br />\n試過入安全模式<br />\n基本上所有功能都用到<br />\n<br />\n其實我都backup左d files <br />\n但因為模擬器入面有d資料想攞返<br />\n但開器到個app<br />\n入安全模式都開唔到模擬器<br />\n<br />\n想問下全能的連登仔<br />\n部腦仲有無得救<br />\n如果拎去d電腦鋪 救唔救得返？"},{"pid":"d6fa172dd8aad7008daabc00001daf632ee885e8","tid":872670,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T02:50:44.000Z","msg":"電腦 apps<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30241ab388988aee0fce3a9b19bd12d3d2e378c3","tid":872670,"uid":86026,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d6fa172dd8aad7008daabc00001daf632ee885e8","tid":872670,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T02:50:44.000Z","msg":"電腦 apps<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T03:20:55.000Z","msg":"笑9我唔係問題<br />\n幫幫手得唔得..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243994519888e8ce95472846a1d905e1d7b1f39a","tid":872670,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30241ab388988aee0fce3a9b19bd12d3d2e378c3","tid":872670,"uid":86026,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d6fa172dd8aad7008daabc00001daf632ee885e8","tid":872670,"uid":5793,"lik